---
title: Cheesy Indian Kumara & Lentil Dosa-Dillas with Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Adding masala paste and Mumbai spice isn’t the only controversial spin we’ve put on these quesadillas. Top half of your tortilla with a
hearty lentil and veggie filling, then flip the other half over and bake it like a sideways burrito. And there you have it! A ‘dosa-dilla’ oozing
with goodness.
